trans-unit.source: Exposes a means of generating client proxy classes for XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Expõe um meio de gerar classes proxy do cliente de serviços Web XML.

trans-unit.source: The interface to an XML Web service is typically described by a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file.
trans-unit.target: A interface para um serviço Web XML normalmente é descrita por um arquivo WSDL Web Services Description Language ().

trans-unit.source: For example, to obtain a WSDL description of a Web service using ASP.NET exposed at `http://localhost/service.asmx`, simply navigate to `http://localhost/service.asmx?WSDL`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo obter uma descrição de WSDL de um serviço Web usando o ASP.NET exposto em `http://localhost/service.asmx`, simplesmente, navegue até `http://localhost/service.asmx?WSDL`.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceDescriptionImporter class allows you to easily import the information contained in a WSDL description into a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: A classe ServiceDescriptionImporter permite importar facilmente as informações contidas em uma descrição de WSDL em uma <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName>objeto.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: By adjusting the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> parameter, you can instruct a ServiceDescriptionImporter instance either to generate a client proxy class that provides the functionality of the Web service by transparently calling it or to generate an abstract class that encapsulates the functionality of the Web service without implementing it.
trans-unit.target: Ajustando o valor de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>parâmetro, você pode instruir a uma instância de ServiceDescriptionImporter para gerar uma classe de proxy de cliente que fornece a funcionalidade do serviço Web chamando-a transparente ou gerar uma classe abstrata que encapsula a funcionalidade do serviço Web sem implementar o proprietário.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The code in the resulting <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit> object can then either be called directly or exported in the language of your choice.
trans-unit.target: O código resultante <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>objeto pode então ser chamado diretamente ou exportado no idioma de sua escolha.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to the collection of <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values to be imported.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> à coleção de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores a serem importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: Use this method to add <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instances to the collection that is to be imported when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Use esse método para adicionar <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>instâncias na coleção que deve ser importado quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>método é chamado.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The two string parameters, `appSettingUrlKey` and `appSettingBaseUrl`, specify how to construct the `Url` property of the XML Web service proxy that is to be generated from the imported <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> value.
trans-unit.target: Os dois parâmetros de cadeia de caracteres `appSettingUrlKey` e `appSettingBaseUrl`, especifique como construir o `Url` propriedade do proxy do serviço da Web em XML que deve ser gerado a partir de importado <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>valor.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingUrlKey` parameter specifies that the `Url` property should be read out of the web.config file's `<appsettings>` section by using the parameter value as the configuration key.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro especifica que o `Url` propriedade deve ser lida fora do arquivo Web. config `<appsettings>` seção usando o valor do parâmetro como a chave de configuração.

trans-unit.source: If the `appSettingUrlKey` parameter is `null` or an empty string, the initial value is determined by the `location` attribute in the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: Se o `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro é `null` ou uma cadeia de caracteres vazia, o valor inicial é determinado pelo `location` atributo no documento WSDL Web Services Description Language ().

trans-unit.source: If the value of <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> is `Server`, an error is raised if you attempt to set the value of the `appSettingUrlKey` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Se o valor de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>é `Server`, um erro será gerado se você tentar definir o valor da `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingBaseUrl` parameter specifies that the initial value for the `Url` property should be constructed from a combination of this parameter value and the URL specified by the `location` attribute in the WSDL document.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingBaseUrl` parâmetro especifica que o inicial valor para o `Url` propriedade deve ser construída a partir de uma combinação desse valor de parâmetro e a URL especificada pelo `location` atributo no documento WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingUrlKey` parameter must also be specified.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro também deve ser especificado.

trans-unit.source: The `Url` property is constructed by combining a relative URL (constructed from the `appSettingBaseUrl` parameter and the WSDL-specified URL) with the URL loaded from the web.config file.
trans-unit.target: O `Url` propriedade é construída, combinando uma URL relativa (construído a partir de `appSettingBaseUrl` parâmetro e a URL especificada pelo WSDL) com a URL carregada do arquivo Web. config.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is `null` or an empty string, the URL is constructed entirely from the value in the web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Se esse parâmetro for `null` ou uma cadeia de caracteres vazia, a URL é construída inteiramente do valor no arquivo Web. config.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instance to add to the collection
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instância a ser adicionada à coleção

trans-unit.source: Sets the initial value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""></xref> property of the proxy class to be generated from the instance represented by the `serviceDescription` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor inicial de <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""> </xref> propriedade da classe proxy a ser gerado a partir de instância representada pelo `serviceDescription` parâmetro.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that it should be generated from the web.config file's <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appsetting>" name="<appsetting>" href=""></xref> section.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que ele deve ser gerado a partir do arquivo Web. config <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appsetting>" name="<appsetting>" href=""> </xref> seção.

trans-unit.source: Sets the initial value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""></xref> property of the proxy class to be generated from the instance represented by the `serviceDescription` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor inicial de <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""> </xref> propriedade da classe proxy a ser gerado a partir de instância representada pelo `serviceDescription` parâmetro.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that it should be constructed from a combination of the value of this parameter and the URL specified by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_location" name="location" href=""></xref> attribute in the WSDL document.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que deve ser construído com uma combinação do valor deste parâmetro e a URL especificada pelo <xref uid="langword_csharp_location" name="location" href=""> </xref> atributo no documento WSDL.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets various options for code generation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define várias opções para geração de código.

trans-unit.source: The CodeGenerationOptions property allows you to specify various options used when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> method is called to generate code.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade CodeGenerationOptions permite que você especificar várias opções usadas quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>método é chamado para gerar código.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can specify whether simple types described in the WSDL are generated as value types or <xref:System.Data.SqlTypes> namespace types, and whether they are generated as properties or fields.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, você pode especificar se os tipos simples descritos no WSDL são gerados como tipos de valor ou <xref:System.Data.SqlTypes>tipos de namespace, e se eles são gerados como propriedades ou campos.</xref:System.Data.SqlTypes>

trans-unit.source: A member or combination of members of the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions"></xref> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Um membro ou uma combinação de membros a <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions"> </xref> enumeração.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the code generator used by the service description importer.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o gerador de código usado pelo importador de descrição de serviço.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator"></xref> interface used by the service description importer to generate proxy code.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator"> </xref> interface usada pelo importador de descrição de serviço para gerar o código de proxy.

trans-unit.source: Compiles a collection of Web references to produce a client proxy or a server stub.
trans-unit.target: Compila uma coleção de referências da Web para gerar um proxy de cliente ou um stub de servidor.

trans-unit.source: The services description document collection in each <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference> member of the `webReferences` collection should contain only <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects.
trans-unit.target: A coleção de documento de descrição de serviços em cada <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference>membro o `webReferences` coleção deve conter apenas <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>e <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>objetos.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference>

trans-unit.source: This method is unable to interpret <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Esse método é capaz de interpretar <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>objetos.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>

trans-unit.source: If any of the XML Web service methods in the `webReferences` collection share custom parameter or return types, those types are also shared among the proxy methods generated.
trans-unit.target: Se qualquer um dos XML Web serviço métodos o `webReferences` coleção compartilhar parâmetro personalizado ou tipos de retorno, esses tipos também são compartilhados entre os métodos de proxy gerados.

trans-unit.source: This is an important advantage over the situation in which each proxy is compiled separately, because in that case such types do not interoperate.
trans-unit.target: Essa é uma vantagem importante sobre a situação em que cada proxy é compilado separadamente, porque o caso em que esses tipos não interoperam.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceCollection"></xref> of Web references to compile.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceCollection"> </xref> de referências da Web para compilar.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> that specifies the code provider.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> que especifica o provedor de código.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> that specifies the unit into which code is compiled.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> que especifica a unidade na qual o código é compilado.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions"></xref> that specifies code generation options.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions"> </xref> que especifica as opções de geração de código.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> of compiler warnings.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"> </xref> de avisos do compilador.

trans-unit.source: Imports the specified <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values, that generates code as specified by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style*> property.
trans-unit.target: Importa especificado <> </> *> valores, que gera código conforme especificado pelo <> </> *> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: After you have specified the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A> values to import and the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> property of the code to generate, call the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> method to initiate code generation.
trans-unit.target: Depois que você especificou o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A>valores para importar e <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>propriedade do código, chame o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import>método para iniciar a geração de código.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: The namespace into which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values are imported.
trans-unit.target: O namespace no qual o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores são importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> instance in which the code that represents the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> value is generated.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> instância na qual o código que representa o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valor é gerado.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"></xref> value that describes any error that occurred; or 0 if no error occurred.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"> </xref> valor que descreve qualquer erro que ocorreu; ou 0 se nenhum erro ocorreu.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the protocol used to access the described XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o protocolo usado para acessar os serviços Web XML descritos.

trans-unit.source: The allowed values of this property are: - "Soap" - "Soap12" - "HttpPost" - "HttpGet" - "HttpSoap" The default value is "Soap", which indicates the SOAP 1.1 standard.
trans-unit.target: Os valores permitidos para essa propriedade são: - "Soap" - "Soap12" - "HttpPost" - "HttpGet" - "HttpSoap" o valor padrão é "Soap", que indica que o padrão de SOAP 1.1.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the case-insensitive name of the protocol to be imported.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.String>que contém o nome de maiusculas e minúsculas do protocolo a ser importado.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"></xref> used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"> </xref> usado pelo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"></xref> object that contains the XML schemas used by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"> </xref> objeto que contém os esquemas XML usados pelo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instâncias de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>coleção.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances to be imported.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instâncias a serem importados.

trans-unit.source: As with any collection that forms a read-only property, members can be added to the collection, removed from the collection, or modified using the methods exposed by the collection.
trans-unit.target: Assim como acontece com qualquer coleção que formam uma propriedade somente leitura, os membros podem ser adicionados à coleção, removido da coleção ou modificadas usando os métodos expostos pela coleção.

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A> method to add members to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode usar o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A>para adicionar membros a esta coleção.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection"></xref> instance that contains the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances slated to be imported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection"> </xref> instância que contém o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instâncias programado para ser importado pelo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"> </xref> instância.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines the style of code (client or server) that is generated when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values are imported.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que determina o estilo de código (cliente ou servidor) que é gerado quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores são importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: If the Style property is set to <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> generates client proxy classes that provide the functionality of the described Web services by calling them.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade de estilo é definida como <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>gera classes de proxy de cliente que fornecem a funcionalidade dos serviços da Web descritos chamando-los.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>

trans-unit.source: If the Style property is set to <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> instance generates abstract classes that represent the functionality of the described XML Web services without implementing them.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade de estilo é definida como <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>instância gera classes abstratas que representam a funcionalidade dos serviços Web XML descritos sem implementá-las.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>

trans-unit.source: You can then implement them by writing classes that inherit from these abstract classes and implement the relevant methods.
trans-unit.target: Você pode implementá-las escrevendo classes que herdam essas classes abstratas e implementam os métodos relevantes.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Uma da <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"> </xref> valores.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"> </xref>.
